Package: transformr
Title: Easy variable transformations in R
Version: 0.2.4
Authors@R: person("Derek", "Damron", email = "damrondm@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: transformr provides lightweight and robust functions for easy variable
    transformations.  Transformations supported include trimming and
    rescaling for numeric variables, regrouping for categorical variables, and
    imputing for both numeric and categorical variables.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.0)
Suggests:
    devtools,
    testthat,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    pander,
    ggplot2
License: file LICENSE
LazyData: true
LinkingTo: Rcpp
Imports:
    Rcpp
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
VignetteBuilder: knitr
